{"tid":1359743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 職訓局職員公開信","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:13:26.000Z","uid":266243,"like":329,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0723f44247c698f76ed018c4e8558d6ce87481","tid":1359743,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一班關心社會的職業訓練局職員，致力為廣大市民服務及教育下一代。<br />\n作為職員，我們有義務及責任教導學生分辨是非黑白。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日於元朗發生的暴力襲擊事件，我們表示極度憤怒及痛心。一群白衣人在元朗港鐵站內無差別攻擊市民，導致多名市民受傷及陷入恐慌，當中包括小童，長者及婦孺，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n香港作為法治之都，但警方視而不見，公然包庇黑社會攻擊平民，挑戰香港人的底線，我們對警方及白衣人的行為予以強烈譴責。不論任何政治立場，勾結黑社會絕對是一件錯事，我們希望警方不要忘記自己在社會上的角色及責任，盡快將所有涉事襲擊者繩之於法，避免同類事件再次發生，挽回市民對警方的信心，以保社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n經過一連串事件後，社會撕裂嚴重。我們促請政府聆聽民意，盡快解決社會上各種問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一班關心社會的職業訓練局職員上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDo0ziH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDo0ziH.jpg&h=8c2dde5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLFqLqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLFqLqt.jpg&h=b48ce7fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"070ddfbd405936921463f01b89454d07c6790f4c","tid":1359743,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b225a7154d832fcb08798d8c00336755bf518d","tid":1359743,"uid":52928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df41cf64f7cbbe1fd290a2b55835d1f59793006","tid":1359743,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif